Simple Steps to toggle message vibration:\n
1) Disable default message application\'s vibrate\n
2) Enable this app\n
3) Add a widget MineMessageVibrator\n
4) Enjoy~\n
\n
Furthermore\n
1) Set vibration mode for incoming messages\n
2) Set a reminder for the unread messages\n
3) Pick a different vibration mode for reminder\n
